            <p>How do I know I'll get a nice tree?</p>
          </div>
          <div class='faq-padding'>
            <p>Good question! Christmas trees are purchased from tree farmer's based on three grades. They are premium grade, #1 grade and #2 grade. Premium grade trees are the "cream of the crop". They are guaranteed to be the best tree's the farmer has grown for that given year. We ONLY purchase and deliver premium grade tree's.</p>
          </div>
