            <p>How should I best care for my tree?</p>
          </div>
          <div class='faq-padding'>
            <p>Add water to your stand immediately when you bring your tree into the house. Keep as far away as possible from heat sources. Check daily to make sure the water does not go below the base of the tree.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='faq-bubble'>
